WEBVTT

00:09:29.418 --> 00:09:30.901
private sector,

00:09:30.925 --> 00:09:32.194
even individuals.

00:09:32.218 --> 00:09:34.162
We all have a role to play.

00:09:34.186 --> 00:09:38.184
Yes, we need to influence
the way we consume,

00:09:38.208 --> 00:09:39.841
the way we commute,

00:09:39.865 --> 00:09:42.501
the way we use our energy.

00:09:43.143 --> 00:09:47.806
And the good thing is that
all of those solutions are available.

00:09:47.830 --> 00:09:52.028
The question is, if we postpone
action by one day,

00:09:52.052 --> 00:09:55.429
there might be thousands
of lives that we will lose,

00:09:55.453 --> 00:09:58.173
but if we postpone it by one year,

00:09:58.197 --> 00:10:02.080
we might be losing again seven million.